21ST CENTURY INSURANCE
21st Century Insurance is an american auto insurance company and is wholly owned by the Farmers Insurance Group of Companies .
They are headquartered in Wilmington , Delaware , and provide private passenger auto insurance in California and Hawaii .
HISTORY Section::::History .
21st Century Insurance was founded in 1958 by Louis W. Foster as an inter - insurance exchange offering auto insurance , primarily in California .
Initially , the company was called 20th Century Insurance .
The company was purchased in 2005 by AIG and then later sold in 2009 to Farmers Insurance Group of Companies .
